<h2>Risk Legacy</h2>

<h3>Problem</h3>
<p>
	Risk legacy is a complex game played over the course of a few months with a group of people. During the game a lot of time is spent tracking and remembering all the information necessary for the game (i.e. who picked which cards, and how many troops each player receives). Even when all of this information can be remembered accurately, the work done to track the information takes away from the game. Our application will allow players of Risk Legacy to track the relevant information of their game while keep their focus on the gameplay
</p>


